<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对了，火箭女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探把手机放回口袋，我们得……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火箭女孩儿看到一个年轻的女人从美罗城购物中心跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人背着小提琴盒子和一个大袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个人应该就是瓦奥莱特·夏普！”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西落在街上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“站住，瓦奥莱特！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦奥莱特看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想要干什么，火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你偷了别人的东西吗？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦奥莱特没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是很有才的音乐家。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听说美罗城交响乐团还邀请你去面试呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你为什么要偷东西呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼！”瓦奥莱特表情很不好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们说我拉得不够好，进不了那个愚蠢的管弦乐队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我就是要给他们看看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我做了会催眠的小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，我比历史上所有的音乐家都要有钱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跳上一辆等在那里的公交车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公交车开走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西紧跟在公交车后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦奥莱特透过车窗瞪着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你阻止不了我！”她大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿出小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一拉小提琴，其他乘客都看着她，眼睛里一片茫然。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦奥莱特从公交车上跳下来，跑向一个拐角。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西正要去追她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，公交车失控了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汽车开进了人行道上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们跑起来，躲在垃圾桶后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人挥着拳头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“公交车司机发疯了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”罗西大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“瓦奥莱特给公交车司机催眠了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她飞快地飞向公交车，拉住它，让它停下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机醒了，眨了眨眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了什么事儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西来不及回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须阻止瓦奥莱特！”她飞向拐角。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦奥莱特跑着穿过一个工地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>工人们在建一栋大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人和女人走在高高的钢梁上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“瓦奥莱特！”罗西大声叫，“停下来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦奥莱特转过身来，露出邪恶的微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拉了几个音符。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西隔得太远，听得不清楚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，瓦奥莱特身边的人都停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面工人的工具掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞快地飞过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抓住被催眠的人，把他们送到了安全的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>工具哐哐掉在人行道上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿，小心！”一个女人叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西抬头一看，一块巨大的钢梁掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西伸手抓住了它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”她松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>正在这时，罗西听到了奇怪的音乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦奥莱特正在拉小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在罗西做出反应之前，一切变得很模糊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！”罗西自言自语道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……变得……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦奥莱特发出邪恶的笑声。“催眠！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>